      "text": ">[https://twitter.com/iamrosema/status/823390149346111488 @iamrosema]: @daigothebeast friend zone ...... 😿 #twitch #tgs2017",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1668221605,
      "updated": 1668221605
